        Overview

        OWC Tested. Quality You Can Trust.

        OWC individually inspects and fully tests every pre-owned computer to confirm full functionality and accurate grading. All refurbishments and/or upgrades are performed by our Apple Certified Technicians. That's why OWC is the most trusted name in Mac refurbishments.

        Experience huge savings on Mac mini!

        With every Mac mini, there is a lot of computing power packed into a space that's a fraction of the size of normal desktop computers. And when purchased through MacSales.com, you can count on all that computing power at a fraction of the price of buying new. Pick up this 2020 Mac mini and experience dramatic savings!

        Powered by an 8-core M1 Apple Silicon Processor

        The future is here. Apple Silicon system on a chip (SoC) processors integrate the CPU, GPU, Neural Engine, I/O, and so much more onto just one tiny chip for incredible performance and power efficiency.

        16GB of Onboard Memory

        This Mac mini already has all the memory you need built-in. Its one upgrade this machine will never need.

        512GB Solid-State Drive

        This machine comes with a 512GB Apple OEM/Factory Solid-State Drive. This SSD brings some serious horsepower to the track. With SSDs operating dramatically faster than hard drives, you will love the performance gains of having this SSD.

        Gigabit Ethernet, Wi-Fi, and Bluetooth Networking

        This Mac mini, in addition to the one RJ-45 port that supports 10/100/1000BASE-T networks, also has a Bluetooth 5.0 and 802.11a/b/g/n/ac Wi-Fi card installed. So you're covered for all your wired and wireless connection needs.

        Includes

        • Apple Mac mini (M1 Series, Late 2020)
        • Power cord
        • Supports up to macOS 26.x Tahoe (Current Version)

        Keyboard and mouse not included

        OWC recommends using a wired keyboard for the initial OS setup, as Bluetooth keyboards sometimes fail to pair until the initial OS setup is complete
